{"tid":340843,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"半學術 - 鼻屎成份題引出人生哲理","createTime":"2017-07-30T09:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T09:57:31.000Z","uid":132186,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"098d701f075bf8e9c5dcd34881b4980f28c60e50","tid":340843,"uid":132186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T09:50:19.000Z","msg":"尋日出完街之後，新一批鼻屎又黑又硬。硬至像實心肉鬆，手感不像一般的，按下沒治愈感，黑至灰塵。<br />\n<br />\n試以三千字論天氣/空氣品質如何影響鼻屎成份乃至產出夏天時令下品鼻屎，再而引出人生哲理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/174954_f47454d1d3644127f42070181a8b9afc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F174954_f47454d1d3644127f42070181a8b9afc.jpg&h=1e4c778f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ddcaa81e708afcabfa9da57419a04a0d9227dc1","tid":340843,"uid":132186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T09:57:31.000Z","msg":"鼻黏膜的空氣中的灰塵混合、硬化之後，就成為鼻屎。"}]}